  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to prove in practice the effectiveness of Atacand 16 mg in
      reducing blood pressure after 4 weeks of administration and the importance of administration
      of adequate doses
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
